@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Home Page";
}


<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Medical Chatbot</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .article-card {
            background-color: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .article-title {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .article-content {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #555;
        }

        .text-center {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="text-center">
        <h1 class="display-4">Will You Thrive Today?</h1>
       
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="article-card">
                    <div class="article-title">Chronic Diseases</div>
                    <div class="article-content">
                        Chronic diseases are long-lasting conditions that can be controlled but not cured. Examples include diabetes, heart disease, and asthma. Regular check-ups and healthy lifestyle choices are essential for managing these conditions effectively.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="article-card">
                    <div class="article-title">Prevention Tips</div>
                    <div class="article-content">
                        Prevention is key in managing chronic diseases. Maintaining a balanced diet, regular exercise, avoiding smoking, and managing stress can significantly reduce the risk of developing chronic conditions.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="article-card">
                    <div class="article-title">Treatment Options</div>
                    <div class="article-content">
                        Treatment for chronic diseases may include medications, lifestyle changes, and therapy. It's crucial to follow your doctor's advice and have regular follow-ups to monitor your health.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" asp-action="Index2">Chat with Doctor</a>
            <a class="btn btn-primary" asp-action="Index3">Chat with Bot Doc</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/2.11.6/umd/popper.min.js"></script>


    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>

